These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, camping
The people have 2 different jobs:  firefighter, paramedic
1. the firefighter is in an even position##4
2. the paramedic is the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | camping | baking |
| Job     | paramedic    | firefighter   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, milk
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, soccer
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | milk | mirinda        |
| Sport      | snowboarding  | soccer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, soul
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, colombian
1. the russian is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | dubstep |
| Nationality   | russian | colombian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite
There 2 different types of food: apricot, cranberry
1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person eating cranberry is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | mirinda      | sprite |
| Food       | apricot | cranberry    |

 #################################

 
