.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, biathlon
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, scooter
1. the person driving the van is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Sport       | biathlon | swimming  |
| Transport   | scooter  | van |

